name: Low Poly Buildings (Multiple Colors and Variations!)
name_original: Low Poly Buildings (Multiple Colors and Variations!)
description:
Hello Everyone! 

I created low poly buildings for your awesome projects. 

You'll get 12 different buildings, in 3 colors and multiple variations, like little extra roof assets or a base. 

I hope you guys like it. 

Stay safe, stay awesome.

Cheers!
